  "text": "where wc,i is the central frequency, and ∆i is the Full-Width Half-Maximum (FWHM) of the spectrum, for i ∈ {d, a} de- noting the donor and acceptor. For the selected values in Table 1 , Förster radius between donor and acceptor R0 is approximately 8nm which is a common result for semiconductor fluorescent molecules [CITATION_1] .",
